The Glenn Beck Radio Show JULY-09-2013 TUES





The Glenn Beck Program

          
Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET        

      

      
The Glenn Beck Program - 07/09/13

Tuesday, July 09, 2013 12:01 PM



Glenn and the guys talk about the IRS and how they may have "accidentally"
 published Social Security #'s.

 Also Glenn discusses his confusion over sports stories and how doesn't "get them" 
  in light of the San Francisco 49ers fans
   and how they are upset over their quarterback wearing a Miami Dolphins hat.

 Author Brad Thor joins the guys to discuss his new book, "Hidden Order"
